elements.name: Login, add a new product, search product, add to cart, and checkout

steps.name: Admin is on the login page
Admin enters valid email "admin@shophub.com" and password "admin123"
Admin clicks the login button
Admin should be redirected to the home page
Admin clicks on the Admin panel
Admin adds a new product with name "Bluetooth Mouse"
Admin selects category "Electronics" and enters price "499"
Admin enters initial stock "20" and product description "Wireless optical mouse"
Admin clicks the Add Product button
Admin click the all Products section
Admin clicks on the search bar
Admin types "Bluetooth Mouse" into the search bar
clicks the search button
Products related to "Bluetooth Mouse" should be displayed
User clicks "Add to Cart" on a displayed product
The product should be added to the shopping cart
User clicks on the cart icon
The cart summary should display the added product with the correct price
User clicks the Checkout button
User should be redirected to the checkout page
User click the Logout button
